<lb n="0424b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424b06" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1306</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0424b07" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0424034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】久安四年寫仁和寺藏本，【乙】久安五年寫高山寺藏本，【丙】文和二年寫高野山寶壽院藏本</note>北斗七星護摩祕要儀<note n="0424035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軌＋（一卷）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424035"><lem wit="【大】">軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">軌一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0424b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424b09" ed="T"/><byline type="Author">大興善寺翻經院灌頂阿闍梨述</byline>
<lb n="0424b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424b1001"><note n="0424036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（或本佛言）＋我【丙】</note><app n="0424036"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">或本佛言我</rdg></app>今為末世薄福眾生故。說是北極七星供
<lb n="0424b11" ed="T"/>養護摩次第儀則。於<note n="0424037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">靜＝淨&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0424037"><lem wit="【大】">靜</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">淨</rdg></app>室中作一水壇。或
<lb n="0424b12" ed="T"/><note n="0424038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">方或圓＝圓或方【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424038"><lem wit="【大】">方或圓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">圓或方</rdg></app>各足一肘。以茅香甘松熏<note n="0424039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陸＋（白交）【甲】，（白）【乙】</note><app n="0424039"><lem wit="【大】">陸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">陸白交</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">陸白</rdg></app>龍腦
<lb n="0424b13" ed="T"/>白檀五味和合泥塗之。其壇<note n="0424040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">場＝即【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424040"><lem wit="【大】">場</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">即</rdg></app>內安著圓爐。
<lb n="0424b14" ed="T"/>飲食果子<note n="0424041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（七）＋分【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424041"><lem wit="【大】">分</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">七分</rdg></app>別置<note n="0424042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之燒＝燒之【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424042"><lem wit="【大】">之。燒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">燒之</rdg></app>食謂<note n="0424043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">飯食＝粥飯腦【甲】，飯腦【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0424043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯食＝粥飯腦【甲】，＝飯腦【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424043"><lem wit="【大】">飯食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">粥飯腦</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">飯腦</rdg></app>果餅
<lb n="0424b15" ed="T"/><note n="0424044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酥＝蘇【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424044"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">蘇</rdg></app>蜜等。但五穀并乳木。隨人命星相<note n="0424045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撿＝換【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424045"><lem wit="【大】">撿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">換</rdg></app>
<lb n="0424b16" ed="T"/>用之。</p>
<lb n="0424b17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424b1701">先啟詞曰　至心奉啟北極七<note n="0424046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔明〕－【甲】</note><app n="0424046"><lem wit="【大】">明</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0424047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娜＝那【甲】，〔娜〕－【乙】</note><app n="0424047"><lem wit="【大】">娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">那</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>羅貪
<lb n="0424b18" ed="T"/><note n="0424048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔狼〕－【丙】</note><app n="0424048"><lem wit="【大】">狼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0424049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">巨＝臣【乙】</note><app n="0424049"><lem wit="【大】">巨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">臣</rdg></app>門祿存文曲廉貞武曲破軍尊星。為
<lb n="0424b19" ed="T"/><note n="0424050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">陀＝施&M062485;【原】，施【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0424050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">陀＝施&M062485;【原】，＝施【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424050"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="施">陀</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">施</rdg></app>主<note n="0424051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">某甲二字甲乙二本作夾註</note><note n="0424051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（某甲）二字本文＝（某甲）二字夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424051"><lem wit="【大】">某甲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><note place="inline">某甲</note></rdg></app>。災厄解脫壽命延長得見百秋。
<lb n="0424b20" ed="T"/>今作曼<note n="0424052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">荼＝茶【甲】</note><app n="0424052"><lem wit="【大】">荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">茶</rdg></app>羅。唯願垂哀降臨此處。納受護
<lb n="0424b21" ed="T"/>摩。擁護施主<note n="0424053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">某甲二字甲乙二本作夾註</note><note n="0424053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（某甲）二字本文＝（某甲）二字夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424053"><lem wit="【大】">某甲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><note place="inline">某甲</note></rdg></app>。災難解脫壽命增長所願
<lb n="0424b22" ed="T"/>從心<note place="inline">三<note n="0424054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">遍＝反【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424054"><lem wit="【大】">遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">反</rdg></app></note>。</p>
<lb n="0424b23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424b2301">次結其印。虛心合掌。以二大指。捻二無名
<lb n="0424b24" ed="T"/>指甲。<note n="0424055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二〕－【丙】</note><app n="0424055"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>中指二小指如蓮葉。二頭指小開
<lb n="0424b25" ed="T"/>屈來去。</p>
<lb n="0424b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424b2601">次誦一字頂輪王真言。并召北斗七星真言。</p>
<lb n="0424b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424b2701">頂<note n="0424056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輪＋（王）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424056"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">輪王</rdg></app>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0424b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424b2801" type="dharani"><note n="0424057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲乙丙三本俱梵字無之</note><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5ED;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慕＝謨【甲】【乙】，莫【丙】</note><note n="0424058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慕＝謨【甲】【乙】，＝莫【丙】</note><app n="0424058"><lem wit="【大】">慕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">謨</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">莫</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">曼</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CA56;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">多＝哆【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424059"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">哆</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd"><app><lem wit="【CBETA】">&SD-A56F;&SD-A5FD;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&SD-D957;</rdg></app></t><t lang="chi">那羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跛＝破【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424060"><lem wit="【大】">跛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">破</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A47C;</t><t lang="chi">左</t></tt>
<lb n="0424b29" ed="T"/>
<pb n="0424c" id="T21.1306.0424c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c01" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0424061"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E17C;</t><t lang="chi">吽</t></tt></p>
<lb n="0424c02" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c03" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424c0301">召北斗真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0424c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424c0401" type="dharani"><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5F0;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">莫＝謨【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424062"><lem wit="【大】">莫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">謨</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A67A;</t><t lang="chi">三</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5E5;</t><t lang="chi">曼</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CA56;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0424059" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">哆</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi">羅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5A9;</t><t lang="chi">曩</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFCF;</t><t lang="chi">翳</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-E0AF;</t><t lang="chi">醯</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6AA;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呬＝枳【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424063"><lem wit="【大】">呬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">枳</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5B5;</t><t lang="chi">頗</t></tt>
<lb n="0424c05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c06" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A8;</t><t lang="chi">賀</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A56F;</t><t lang="chi">那</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A440;</t><t lang="chi">迦</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi">伊</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0424061" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-CFC7;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔伊〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424064"><lem wit="【大】">伊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-AAF4;</t><t lang="chi"><yin><zi>謨<app source="0424061" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></zi><sg><note n="0424065" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【乙】</note><app n="0424065"><lem wit="【大】">二合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></sg></yin></t></tt>
<lb n="0424c07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c08" ed="T"/><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A557;</t><t lang="chi">哆</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0424061" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A464;</t><t lang="chi">伽</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A5FD;</t><t lang="chi"><app source="0424061" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">羅</rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6B2;</t><t lang="chi">唅</t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-DA49;</t><t lang="chi">娑<note n="0424066" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00085;＋（二合）夾註【甲】</note><app n="0424066"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00085;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app></t></tt><tt><t lang="san-sd">&SD-A6A9;</t><t lang="chi"><note n="0424067" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝賀【甲】【丙】，賀引【乙】</note><note n="0424067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝賀【甲】【丙】，＝賀引【乙】</note><app n="0424067"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">賀</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">賀引</rdg></app></t></tt></p>
<lb n="0424c09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0424c10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0424c1001">以手<note n="0424068" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">取＋（命）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424068"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">取命</rdg></app>木及穀并<app source="0424044" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">蘇</rdg></app><note n="0424069" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蜜＝密【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424069"><lem wit="【大】">蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">密</rdg></app>油等。擲之於爐內
<lb n="0424c11" ed="T"/>火燒之。<note n="0424070" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＝目【甲】</note><app n="0424070"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">目</rdg></app>專視其本命之星。若動搖變色。
<lb n="0424c12" ed="T"/><note n="0424071" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔光照通〕－【丙】</note><app n="0424071"><lem wit="【大】">光<note n="0424072" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔照通〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0424072"><lem wit="【大】">照通</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>爍<note n="0424073" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光貌＝光色&M062485;【原】，〔光貌〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424073"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="光色">光貌</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>黃白者。<note n="0424074" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＋（為）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424074"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">即為</rdg></app>應願如<note n="0424075" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＝未即【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424075"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">未即</rdg></app>依
<lb n="0424c13" ed="T"/>前法七日夜而為之。必應如事不即其星藏
<lb n="0424c14" ed="T"/>沒不見<note place="inline">決云<note n="0424076" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＋（可）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0424076"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">不可</rdg></app>求也</note>謂北斗七星者日月五星之精
<pb n="0425a" id="T21.1306.0425a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0425a01" ed="T"/>也。曩括七曜照臨八方上曜於天神下直于
<lb n="0425a02" ed="T"/>人間。以司善惡而分禍福。群星所朝宗萬靈
<lb n="0425a03" ed="T"/>所俯仰。若有人能禮拜供養長壽福貴。不信
<lb n="0425a04" ed="T"/>敬者運命不久。是以祿命書云。世有司命神
<lb n="0425a05" ed="T"/>每至庚<note n="0425001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">申＝辛【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425001"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">辛</rdg></app>日。上向天帝<note n="0425002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（所）＋陳【甲】</note><app n="0425002"><lem wit="【大】">陳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">所陳</rdg></app>說眾人之罪惡。
<lb n="0425a06" ed="T"/>重罪者則<note n="0425003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徹＝撤【甲】【乙】，擲【丙】</note><note n="0425003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徹＝撤【甲】【乙】，＝擲【丙】</note><app n="0425003"><lem wit="【大】">徹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">撤</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">擲</rdg></app>算。輕罪者則去紀。算<note n="0425004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">書＝盡【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425004"><lem wit="【大】">書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">盡</rdg></app>紀<note n="0425005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告即主＝告即至【甲】，失即至【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0425005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告即主＝告即至【甲】，＝失即至【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425005"><lem wit="【大】">告
<lb n="0425a07" ed="T"/>即主</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">告即至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">失即至</rdg></app>命<note n="0425006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">已＝亡最好&M062403;【原】，亡【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0425006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝亡最好&M062403;【原】，＝亡【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425006"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">亡最好</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">亡</rdg></app>者。是故如來為末世薄福短命夭
<lb n="0425a08" ed="T"/>死眾生故。說是一字頂輪王召北斗七星供
<lb n="0425a09" ed="T"/>養護摩之儀則。為供養者。令其<note n="0425007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">屬命＝命屬【丙】</note><app n="0425007"><lem wit="【大】">屬命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">命屬</rdg></app>星數削
<lb n="0425a10" ed="T"/>死籍還付生籍。若諸國王於自宮中作曼茶
<lb n="0425a11" ed="T"/>羅。如法護摩禮拜供養。北斗歡喜為擁護故。
<lb n="0425a12" ed="T"/>久居勝位琩安穩。后妃夫人後宮<note n="0425008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綵＝婇【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425008"><lem wit="【大】">綵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">婇</rdg></app>女。王
<lb n="0425a13" ed="T"/>子群臣三公百官。上下和穆不行非法。人民
<lb n="0425a14" ed="T"/>熾盛稼穡豐饒國土安寧。無有災難不現<note n="0425009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怪異＝異怪【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0425009"><lem wit="【大】">怪
<lb n="0425a15" ed="T"/>異</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">異怪</rdg></app>。疫病死<note n="0425010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">亡＝市【乙】</note><app n="0425010"><lem wit="【大】">亡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">市</rdg></app>不起。境內怨敵群賊自然退
<lb n="0425a16" ed="T"/>散。故以是法甚為祕要。</p>
<lb n="0425a17" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>北斗七<note n="0425011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">星＋（護摩）【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0425011"><lem wit="【大】">星</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">星護摩</rdg></app>祕要儀<note n="0425012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軌＝則一卷【甲】</note><app n="0425012"><lem wit="【大】">軌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">則一卷</rdg></app><note n="0425013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書云久安四年七月二十八日於高野奉傳受了，乙本奧書云（朱書）嘉承二年二月十三日於禪定房以御本移點了同日御房受奉了，一校了僧林寬之本，久安五年二月二十一日辰時許樂生房奉受了僧&CB10923;信，丙本奧書云文和二年癸未二月二十七日申&CB00018;於神護寺成身院書寫畢宣澄二十四歲</note></jhead></juan></div1>
